[glow=black,2,300][i] Router Name:[b]WRT54G[/b] Host Name:[b]AwzomeScape[/b] Domain Name: *blank* MTU:[b]Auto[/b] Size:1500
Local IP Address: [b]192.168.1.1[/b] subnet mask: [b]225.225.225.0[/b] DHCP Server: [b]enabled[/b] Starting IP Address: [b]192.168.1.100[/b] ....(more usless things) [/i][/glow]
i have a folder with all my things for the server (client, compiler etc.)
but... now what?
pleeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeease help thank you
